ActCanada Labour Code
PrecisAppointment of ANDRÉ LEVACALIER of Dollard-des-Ormeaux, Quebec, to be a part-time member of the Canada Industrial Relations Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and order that ANDRÉ LECAVALIER be deemed to be employed in the Public Service for the purposes of the Public Service Superannuation Act.
